    <item>
      <title>特朗普媒体怀疑论者被做空股票，面临艰难的战斗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-media-djt-skeptics-who-get-shares-to-short-face-uphill-battle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的媒体初创公司的股票是美国押注成本最高的股票之一。作为衡量成本的一个指标，一项粗略计算显示，该股需要在下周下跌 12%，卖空者才能收支平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-media-djt-skeptics-who-get-shares-to-short-face-uphill-battle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 12:23:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>未经授权的人工智能语音克隆泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 从 TikTok 中去除脸部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/unauthorized-ai-voice-clones-of-taylor-swift-face-removal-from-tiktok</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 与环球音乐集团 (Universal Music Group NV) 的新协议包含一项关键条款：该视频应用程序同意删除由人工智能创建的未经授权的音乐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/unauthorized-ai-voice-clones-of-taylor-swift-face-removal-from-tiktok</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 12:11:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
